<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC4FFA161D0F8E5C4CFF8C9" bold="true" box="[151,404,1842,1869]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">
Records from 
<collectingCountry id="F31E50C9FFC4FFA1600AF8E4C4D4F8C9" box="[333,399,1842,1868]" name="India" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">India</collectingCountry>
.
</emphasis>
<collectingRegion id="49CDDEBBFFC4FFA160E7F8E5C7FCF8C8" box="[416,679,1843,1869]" country="India" name="Andhra Pradesh" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">ANDHRA PRADESH</collectingRegion>
: Visakhapatnam (reported as 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC4FFA16540F8E5C588F8F4" authority="Bartsch 1989" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1989" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Rhombognathus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="papuensis">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC4FFA16540F8E5C061F8C9" box="[1031,1338,1843,1869]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">Rhombognathus papuensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC4FFA16400F8E5C588F8F4" author="Bartsch, I." pageId="8" pageNumber="309" pagination="138 - 148" refId="ref8522" refString="Bartsch, I. (1989) New species of Copidognathus (Acari: Halacaridae) from Hawaiian Islands. Occasional Papers, Bernice P. Bishop Museum, 29, 138 - 148." type="journal article" year="1989">Bartsch 1989</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
), among rocky algae— 
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC4FFA1609FF881C7F4F8F4" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[472,687,1878,1905]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" pagination="282 - 286" refId="ref10062" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1995 c) Record of three species of Rhombognathus (Halacaridae: Acari) from Indian Ocean region. Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 92, 282 - 286." type="journal article" year="1995">Chatterjee (1995c)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<collectingRegion id="49CDDEBBFFC4FFA163FCF881C636F8F4" box="[699,877,1879,1905]" country="India" name="Tamil Nadu" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">TAMIL NADU</collectingRegion>
: Kanya Kumari (=Cape Comorin) (reported as 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC4FFA164C3F881C45CF811" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1989" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Rhombognathus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="papuensis">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC4FFA164C3F881C45CF811" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">R. papuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), among rocky algae— 
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC4FFA1634BF8ADC7B9F810" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[524,738,1914,1941]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" pagination="282 - 286" refId="ref10062" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1995 c) Record of three species of Rhombognathus (Halacaridae: Acari) from Indian Ocean region. Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 92, 282 - 286." type="journal article" year="1995">Chatterjee (1995c)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<collectingRegion id="49CDDEBBFFC4FFA163ABF8ADC639F810" box="[748,866,1915,1941]" country="India" name="Kerala" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">KERALA</collectingRegion>
: Kovalam (reported as 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC4FFA16523F8ADC1A8F811" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1989" box="[1124,1267,1915,1940]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Rhombognathus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="papuensis">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC4FFA16523F8ADC1A8F811" box="[1124,1267,1915,1940]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">R. papuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), among rocky algae— 
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC4FFA161ABF849C4E1F83C" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[236,442,1950,1977]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" pagination="282 - 286" refId="ref10062" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1995 c) Record of three species of Rhombognathus (Halacaridae: Acari) from Indian Ocean region. Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 92, 282 - 286." type="journal article" year="1995">Chatterjee (1995c</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC4FFA16082F849C754F83F" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[453,527,1951,1978]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" pagination="107 - 108" refId="ref10142" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1996 b) Ciliate infestation on phytal Halacaridae (Acari) from the Kovalam beach (Kerala coast). Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 93, 107 - 108." type="journal article" year="1996">1996b</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB61059FFC4FFA06180F815C61BFF50" blockId="8.[151,1437,1842,2013]" lastBlockId="9.[151,1436,151,213]" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="310" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC4FFA16180F815C46FF858" bold="true" box="[199,308,1987,2013]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">Remarks</emphasis>
. Although this 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC4FFA160A6F815C7ABF858" box="[481,752,1987,2013]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC4FFA160A6F815C7CCF858" box="[481,663,1987,2013]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">Rhombognathus</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
is closely related to 
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC4FFA1629FF815C135F859" box="[984,1134,1987,2012]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC4FFA1629FF815C131F859" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1989" box="[984,1130,1987,2012]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Rhombognathus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="papuensis">R. papuensis</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
there are some differences in need to be studied in detail to determine its exact identity. 
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC5FFA06200FF41C141FF37" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[839,1050,151,178]" pageId="9" pageNumber="310" pagination="107 - 108" refId="ref10142" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1996 b) Ciliate infestation on phytal Halacaridae (Acari) from the Kovalam beach (Kerala coast). Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 93, 107 - 108." type="journal article" year="1996">Chatterjee (1996b)</bibRefCitation>
reported ciliate infestation on this species (cited as 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC5FFA06013FF6DC4B8FF51" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1989" box="[340,483,187,212]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Rhombognathus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="9" pageNumber="310" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="papuensis">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC5FFA06013FF6DC4B8FF51" box="[340,483,187,212]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="310">R. papuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) from Kovalam beach, 
<collectingRegion id="49CDDEBBFFC5FFA063A9FF6DC667FF50" box="[750,828,187,213]" country="India" name="Kerala" pageId="9" pageNumber="310">Kerala</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
